My Pregnancy is a week-by-week pregnancy tracker. Our app will help you over the course of your pregnancy. Stay on top of the changes happening inside your body. Find out how your baby is developing.

Our app is completely free and does not contain advertising.

This app includes:
- week-by-week advice;
- useful information on fetal development and changes in your body;
- week-by-week fetal measurements and imaging;
- a to-do list for each trimester;
- a list of things you will need for hospital check-in, post-natal care and check-out;
- a weight tracker you can use to follow weight gain;
- a kick counter;
- a contraction timer;
- and much more

We have created this app with love, specially for young mothers.

This app is not intended for medical use and is not a substitute for medical consultation.

If you have any questions or requests, please write to neumandev@gmail.com. We are eager to hear your comments on how to improve the app.

Deliver a healthy baby with doctors' consultations, 150+ Tips and Articles for a healthy pregnancy from medical experts, and 20+ tools in the app.

Our community helps each other within 24 hours for free. 
If you need psychological support you can ask an anonymous question in the app and get support and answer quickly.
At a time when clinics are closed and hospitals are overcrowded - you should not be alone with your problems and questions!

PREGNANCY TOOLS:
–‍ Online consultations with doctors;
– Pregnancy tracker: tips and tricks week by week;
– Important notifications / reminders: when to register, get screened and visit a doctor;
– Answers to all questions about the pregnancy week by week;
– The official list of things from maternity hospitals in your city;
– Free contraction counter (contraction timer);
– Pregnancy diary: keep information about your pregnancy;
– Dynamics of changes and weight log;
– Baby visualization. Cognitive comparisons to the fruit sizes.
– Kick counter (movement counter). Control the movements of your baby to prevent oxygen starvation and other risks;
– Control of changes in the body and Symptoms. Find out what to expect at each stage;
– Prenatal Yoga;
– Useful videos: how to prepare for childbirth, how to breathe correctly, how to give birth without tearing, how to introduce the first complementary foods, how to apply to the breast and many other useful videos;
– Visits to the doctor. Schedule visits and questions for the doctor. Save analyzes and visit history;
– Music for the child. A large collection of soothing tunes, sleep music and classical music for the proper development of the child.
– Maternity Diary. Store all photos and videos of your most memorable events in the app.

We strive to create the most useful app so that you can manage your pregnancy correctly, give birth to healthy babies, and give them the correct upbringing!

Managing pregnancy in the Supermoms club is your right choice!

A healthy nation is a confident future!

Join us!

ANATOMIA – SUPERA 

Este é um aplicativo de realidade aumentada, desenvolvido em 3D, que explora a anatomia do corpo humano. 

Destinado, com exclusividade, para uso de médicos em seus estudos e elucidações sobre a estrutura dessa articulação.

Para visualizar os modelos em realidade aumentada, deve-se baixar este aplicativo e posicionar a câmera do celular ou tablet na imagem “ANATOMIA – PÉ", impressa na frente da lâmina (física) de ARCOXIA, previamente entregue aos médicos.

Com navegação intuitiva, a interação se dá de forma simples (obrigatoriamente a partir da leitura da lâmina física), por meio deste aplicativo:

- Posicione a câmera do celular ou tablet na imagem “ANATOMIA - PÉ";

– O ícone em formato de losango, no topo da tela, ativa e desativa as legendas, ocultas nos pontos inseridos em cada imagem;

– As setas ajudam a navegar entre as imagens;

– Tanto o zoom quanto a rotação das imagens são feitos por meio de toques na tela.

Tudo muito fácil e prático!
